 \mathopen {}\left \lvert \mathcal {B} a\right \rvert \mathclose {}
 with edges in b \approx _{\mathcal {B} a} \mathsf {rx}_{\mathcal {A}}{a}^*b' and reflexivity data for b:Ba given by \Phi _B ab\colon  b\approx _{\mathcal {B} a}\mathsf {rx}_{\mathcal {A}}{a}^*b is univalent.

