 \mathopen {}\left \lvert \mathcal {A}\right \rvert \mathclose {}
\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}} x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y is a proposition, or (equivalently), is contractible with centre 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,\mathsf {rx}_{\mathcal {A}}{x}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
. We shall refer to a univalent reflexive graph as a path object.

